OL,6,FSo it is important to ensure these
OL,7,Fbulletins are not dropped except in
OL,8,Fthe most exceptional of circumstances.
OL,10,FToday there are no regional bulletins
OL,11,Fon ITV 1. FA Cup coverage runs from
OL,12,F3.30pm until 7pm. There is also no
OL,13,Fearly evening network news.
OL,15,FSome clarity is needed on regulatory
OL,16,Frequirements.
OL,18,FShould Ofcom require ITV to schedule
OL,19,Fregional news every day, except on the
OL,20,Flikes of Christmas Day and Boxing Day?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/6
