OL,6,FOr is it ok to to drop the bulletins
OL,7,Ffor scheduling reasons, as long as
OL,8,Fannual volumes are met?
OL,10,FIf ITV believes there is no demand for
OL,11,Fweekend regional news bulletins it
OL,12,Fshould have the courage to say so.
OL,13,FThen it could officially drop them and
OL,14,Fshift resources elsewhere.
OL,16,FTo be fair, the BBC has sometimes
OL,17,Fdropped its teatime regional news at
OL,18,Fweekends because of live sport.
