OL,6,FOn Sundays the late bulletin has still
OL,7,Fbeen shown as normal. On Saturdays the
OL,8,Fsole mid evening bulletin has moved to
OL,9,Flunchtime or the late evening.
OL,11,F(Exceptionally the nations have shown
OL,12,Funplanned late Saturday bulletins
OL,13,Fbecause of major stories.)
OL,15,FBut back to ITV.
OL,17,FThe regional news is ITV's principle
OL,18,Flicence commitment. Indeed local news
OL,19,Fand current affairs is the only
OL,20,Fregional commitment in England.
