OL,7,Fexpediency does not suggest that the
OL,8,Fspirit of this commitment is being
OL,9,Ffully honoured by the company.
OL,11,FOfcom needs to make sure weekend
OL,12,Fbulletins are mandatory ` except in
OL,13,Ftruly exceptional circumstances.
OL,15,FOr ITV should be allowed to drop them
OL,16,Fas long as if makes up for this in
OL,17,Fsome other way.
